text: Introducing this impeccably maintained & expansive residence nestled in Highland Greens! Step into the welcoming embrace of a three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home featuring an open-concept main level leading seamlessly to a delightful patio & fully fenced backyard. The heart of the home boasts a charming kitchen with a walk-in pantry, double oven, quartz countertops, & stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, retreat to the sizable primary bedroom with a walk-in closet & luxurious five-piece bathroom. Additionally, discover two generous bedrooms, a full hall bath, a convenient laundry room, & a versatile bonus room/loft area on the upper level. Stay cool & comfortable with central air conditioning, perfect for the upcoming summer months!

ASSUMABLE 3.25% VA LOAN! Move in ready daylight basement rambler boasting 2, 118sq.ft. of living space on a spacious .53acre lot. Covered front patio entry leads to foyer entry. Main floor features vaulted great room w/ cozy f/p & slider to rear deck overlooking greenbelt. Quartz kitchen w/ lots of cabinet & counter space & formal dining room. Bedroom & 1/2 bath on main. Fully finished basement features 2nd living room w/ slider to large rear trex deck, primary suite w/ 3/4 bath & oversize closet, additional bedroom w/ full guest bath. Full laundry room w/ soaking sink. Oversize 576sq.ft. garage & driveway parking. Conveniently located w/ quick commute to I5, shopping, dining & schools. Ask about the assumable loan & save on this home!

Welcome home to this darling bungalow in Lyman! This charming home isn't built like all those cookie cutter floor plans! Check out the warm and cozy the living room perfect to invite guests in with free standing woodstove, an excellent heat source on a cool PNW evening. Conveniently located near the dining room and living room, this efficient kitchen is complete with oak cabinets, tiled backsplash behind the sink, newer appliances that stay with the home and lots of storage. Each bedroom has a large closet for storage, windows for sunlight and ample space for furniture. The primary suite is complete with a full bath shower combo and big walk-in closet. The large shop is perfect for any home project, storing RV's, boats, car projects & more!

Located in the historic neighborhood of Cap Sante, a welcoming wrap-around front porch enjoys beautiful channel views & leads to an interior of gleaming wood & intricate detailing. Gourmet kitchen is open to both family room and a sun dappled breakfast room; elegant living and dining rooms. Four en-suite bedrooms; Owner's suite w/views and private retreat space. Guest cottage w/full kitchen & 3/4 bath. Double car garage/shop/over sized lot; walking distance to the marina, waterfront & all downtown amenities. So many upgrades, this perfectly located home is turn-key.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Recently remodeled & move in ready this charming split level is tucked away on a quite side street, yet near to all things Anacortes! Be welcomed home by a light & bright living room complete with fireplace for cool evenings, gleaming vinyl plank flooring & designer finishes. Living flows to open dining & delightful kitchen with slider to a large deck & your own backyard oasis. Chefs kitchen features ample storage, beautiful tile backsplash & plenty of counter space for prep work. Primary suite & 2 more beds on upper as well as 2 full baths. Lower level houses a flex space ideal for office or family room as well as utility room & garage entrance. Fully fenced backyard is perfect for a mellow moment around the firepit. Truly a must see!

Dramatic panoramic views of the Guemes Channel from this desirable building lot perched above the water. Imagine expansive windows of your new contemporary dream home watching boats gracefully travel the channel framed by the Cascade mountains with views all the way to Canada. The perfect backdrop to build your relaxing PNW haven. Enjoy painted sunset views over the San Juan Islands. A blank canvas of limitless possibilities awaiting creativity and imagination. Architectural drawings help show what transformation may be possible, bringing your design to reality.

Beautiful rambler in the River's Edge neighborhood! This Four Bedroom, 1.75 Bath is everything you have been looking for! Open concept Family Room, Kitchen & eating area provides plenty of space for entertaining your friends and loved ones. The cook will love the Kitchen area with the stainless appliances, gas cooktop, pull out drawers for easy storage & an island big enough for a crowd. Cozy backyard fully fenced for your privacy and minimal maintenance. Three car garage provides plenty of space to park and still have room for a shop or home gym. A/C too! A short walk from the local boat launch & just minutes away from parks, restaurants & Burlington shopping.

Lovely 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom country cottage directly across the street from the Skagit River and nestled amongst mature trees. Comfortable open kitchen/living area with large windows. Spacious wrap-around deck with river views. Newer roof 2 years ago on house and garage. Sold with furniture. House was raised above the flood plain several years ago.

Custom-built 1800 sqft , 3bed/2bath home with unparalleled privacy, craftsmanship, and meticulous maintenance nestled on serene acreage. For peace of mind, a security system is installed; power continuity is assured with a whole-house generator. Remain comfortable through all seasons with your heat pump, propane furnace, wood stove, and a sealed crawlspace to enhance energy efficiency. Property features a shop with ample space for hobbies and projects. Other outbuildings offer generous storage options as well as dedicated RV storage. Outdoors, this haven has fruit trees and expansive garden space. To enhance your enjoyment, there is a large deck, firepit, and hot tub. Dont miss this opportunity to make this sanctuary your home!

Escape to paradise at this exquisite Lake Cavanaugh waterfront retreat! Spanning 3, 000 square feet, this home offers a seamless blend of luxury and comfort, showcasing stunning lake views from every angle. Entertain with ease in the spacious, open-concept living areas, where large windows flood the space with natural light and frame picturesque scenes of the serene waters. Step outside to the expansive deck and envision hosting the ultimate Fourth of July celebration. Boating enthusiasts will delight in the convenience of the hydraulic boat lift. Whether you're fishing, water skiing, or simply cruising along the shoreline, this property offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment.

3 bedroom home with detached garage and DADU. Main house has a spacious kitchen with plenty of room to work. Cozy living room, den and formal dining area. Large lot, plenty of room for parking and still room for your RV and boat. Low maintenance back yard offers it ALL! Garden space, patio with pergola, swimming pool, playset, firepit and dog area too! Large, detached garage with plenty of space for parking or hobbies. Located close to Hwy 20 makes commuting easy, and convenient to downtown shopping and restaurants. Come check it out!

Experience comfortable living, stunning three-bedroom, 2332sqft home w/large 3 car garage in desirable Cambridge Commons. Open & spacious kitchen w/central island and dining area, enjoy evenings by the gas fireplace in living room. Retreat to the main level primary bedroom w/bathroom & walk-in closet. Need a quiet space to work or relax? Look no further - The den/office provides the perfect solution, along with a separate laundry room for added functionality. Upstairs, discover two good sized bedrooms, a full bath, and a bonus room, providing ample space for relaxation and recreation. Fully fenced backyard, complete w/covered patio, perfect for entertaining. Community includes a fenced dog park and neighborhood park with playground.

Welcome to Samish Island living! This highly desirable area is home to a vibrant community with a focus on arts, music and peaceful living. The 8, 712 square foot lot is ready for you to create your new home, with slightly sloped views of Samish Bay to the north. This property includes private shared beach access just down the block for launching kayaks and canoes or just a walk on the beach. Amenities on Samish Island include the public beach, Samish Island Park which includes playground, tennis and more. Events include the Samish Island Arts Festival, potlucks, parades and all-island garage sale! And just minutes away from the eccentric town of Edison with great food and festivals, Bayview hiking trails and the beautiful Chuckanut Drive.

Looking for quiet country living? Come view this beautiful home nestled on 5 private acres in a parklike setting in desirable Prairie Acres community! This home is 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2, 472 sf and offers an open floor plan w/ living room, dining room & family room w/a cozy propane stove. The kitchen features granite counters, an island, eating bar, pantry and tons of storage. There is a flex room/office off the family room with built in cabinetry. The primary bedroom suite is huge & features an ensuite bath & large walk-in closet. Enjoy relaxing on the huge covered deck overlooking the fully fenced backyard. House has A/C & wired for a generator. Detached garage, several outbuildings, covered RV/boat parking too! This one is a must see!

Just under 22 acres and two parcels this forested lot is immersed in nature yet less than 10 minutes to I-5. This lot has endless possibilities. Property backs up to Butler Creek and has a small stream running through. Bring your builder and your imagination to get started on your dream home today.

Step into modern luxury with this like-new gem! You'll love the open layout, seamlessly connecting the spacious living room, dining area & well-appointed kitchen w/a slider opening onto the backyard. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, pantry, quartz counters, center island, & ample counter space for all your cooking needs. Retreat to the generously sized primary suite, flooded w/natural light, & enjoy the spa-like en-suite featuring a double vanity, soaker tub, walk-in shower, & oversized walk-in closet. Each bedroom offers a bright & airy ambiance & plenty of closet space along w/added ease of an upstairs laundry. Savor summer evenings in the privacy of your fully fenced backyard & enjoy the convenience of a full-size 2-car garage.

Come see this hidden gem! Conveniently nestled in trees at the end of a dead end street, this nearly half acre lot is secluded, but also steps from a charming, walkable neighborhood, and minutes from the water. Inside you will find vaulted ceilings and an open living space flooded with natural light from ample windows, throughout. A large loft features an on suite bathroom and walk-in closet. A 2nd bedroom and updated bathroom can be found on the main level. In the partially finished basement you will find a 3rd bedroom with a separate outdoor entrance, perfect for an office, guest room, or flex space. Surrounded by nature, the upper deck and lower patio are ready for entertaining. Turn key with brand new roof- 5/24! Come make it your own.

The Lopez at Highpoint East will surely steal your heart. At 1, 785 sf this cozy 3 BD, 1 3/4 BA home has a bonus room with French Doors (perfect for office or den) and lofty 11' ceilings in the living room and kitchen. You'll cook up a storm in the island kitchen, so efficiently designed with quartz countertops and stainless and black appliances. Enjoy your landscaped, fenced and irrigated 140' deep yard with a Timber Tech rear deck perfect for relaxing and entertaining.

Gorgeous remodeled home w ocean and island views. Fully remodeled light-filled main level w plank flooring features an open floor plan w high ceiling, wood beam accents, & plenty of windows & skylights. Entertain & enjoy the views from the spacious dining rm & living rm w floor to ceiling stone fireplace surround. Primary bedroom features heated floors & stunning bath w dual vanity & large walk-in glass & tile shower. Downstairs is an equally spacious living area w a second kitchen ready for your personal touch. Laundry/mud room w folding counter & plenty of storage. Outside enjoy views from the deck as well as pear, cherry, & apple trees, garden space, fire pit & plenty of parking space. Mini split for heat & A/C plus generator.

This beautifully maintained rambler is located in a sought-after neighborhood close to downtown Burlington. Inside, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms, one is a primary suite with an updated 3/4 bathroom. A well-lit formal living room, family room, and dining room open to gourmet kitchen overlooking your beautifully landscaped fully fenced back and side yard. Attached is a fully enclosed Sunroom and large entertainment deck, detached storage building w/power, 2-car garage with storage and cabinets. So much more to list, stop by and see. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home in an excellent location, off Hwy 20, for convenient access to shopping and I-5.

Plans and permits for Townhomes on Waugh Road; four-plex & triplex for a total of seven units on a single parcel. All utilities (sewer, PUD water, Cascade natural gas, PSE, Comcast, Verizon telephone), are to the site. Curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and curb cuts per City specifications, plus mailbox kiosk and off-site storm retention pond provided to the north according to City requirements. Nice territorial and mountain views from a level lot!

Plans and permit for a four-plex townhome on Waugh Road. All utilities (sewer, PUD water, Cascade natural gas, PSE, Comcast, Verizon telephone), are to the site. Curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and curb cuts per City specifications, plus mailbox kiosk and off-site storm retention pond provided to the north according to City requirements. Nice territorial and mountain views from a level lot!

This bank-owned 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1, 344 square foot manufactured home is located in Hamilton, Washington along the North Cascades Highway (20) & Skagit River Valley. Hamilton is a 30 minute drive west to Mt. Vernon & I-5. The home is on a 1/3 acre lot along Bella Street, which is south of Highway 20, & was built in 1991. It has an open floor plan with kitchen/dining & living room. Primary bedroom & bathroom are at the western end and the other two bedrooms at the eastern end. There are two enclosed porches and two uncovered decks on the front and rear of the home. A 960 square foot shop & two small storage sheds are on the lot. The home is in need of repair & renovation. The sale is AS IS. The lot includes two small shed buildings.

[DUPLEX IN DOWNTOWN MOUNT VERNON] Excellent multi-family property for an investor! Great location- within walking distance to shopping and restaurants in downtown Mount Vernon. Unit A & B - 650SQFT each. Additional mobile home in the back of the lot is rented as well. Call with questions.
